com.sharneng.lookup.fluent

Interface Sourced<E,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of the source data
    T - the element type of the lookup being built
    All Superinterfaces:
    Indexing<E,T>, Selected<E,T>

    public interface Sourced<E,T>
extends Selected<E,T>
    Represent a stage of the fluent API that the source data is provided for building a Lookup instance.
